text: @FedExHelp, I have encountered few companies with service bad as Fedex Express Israel.  They (dishonestly) did not deliver as they claimed to have attempted, and were rude on the phone, and made me run around in loops to get package (still waiting). New low for Israeli service.

@ariheist Hello Ari, this is Rochelle. I'm sorry to hear that you're displeased with your FedEx experience. I am a U.S. representative and can assist if your package is traveling within the U.S. If you need international assistance, I can provide the contact information for your country.
@ariheist Please DM your tracking number, delivery address and telephone number. --Rochelle
